    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="Markdown一些常用命令"><a href="#Markdown一些常用命令" class="headerlink" title="Markdown一些常用命令"></a>Markdown一些常用命令</h2><pre><code>1.设置标题级别标题前加几个#，就代表几级标题一级标题#标题二级标题##标题2.引用&gt; 亚里士多德说过，人生最终的价值在于觉醒和思考，而不仅仅在于生存。3.写无序列表- 无序列表- 无序列表4.有序列表数字+英文句号5.插入图片![中秋](http://pic128.huitu.com/res/20190901/571787_20190901124015978020_1.jpg)6.创建超链接[baidu](https://www.baidu.com)7.加粗**加粗**8.斜体*斜体*9.调整字体、字号和颜色    &quot;&lt;font face=&quot;微软雅黑&quot; color=&quot;red&quot; size=&quot;28&quot;&gt;字体、颜色和字号&lt;/font&gt;&quot;    &lt;font face=&quot;微软雅黑&quot; color=&quot;red&quot; size=&quot;28&quot;&gt;字体、颜色和字号&lt;/font&gt;10.居中、居左、居右（适用于字体、图片）居中&lt;center&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;微软雅黑&quot; color=&quot;red&quot; size=&quot;28&quot;&gt;字体、颜色和字号&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/center&gt;居左&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;微软雅黑&quot; color=&quot;red&quot; size=&quot;28&quot;&gt;字体、颜色和字号&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</code></pre><hr><center><font faceface="微软雅黑" color="green" size="14">**music**</font></center><center><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="330" height="86" src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=481356667&auto=1&height=66"></iframe></center><center><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="330" height="86" src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=413812448&auto=0&height=66"></iframe></center><hr><blockquote><center><font faceface="微软雅黑" color="green" size="12">孔子曾说过:“言必信,行必果”</font></center></blockquote><hr><center><font faceface="微软雅黑" color="green" size="14">**video**</font></center><hr><h2 id="参考文献"><a href="#参考文献" class="headerlink" title="参考文献"></a>参考文献</h2><p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/av23983281" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av23983281</a><br><a href="https://walesexcitedmei.github.io/2018/08/29/HEXO-hexo-%E4%B8%AD%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://walesexcitedmei.github.io/2018/08/29/HEXO-hexo-%E4%B8%AD%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</a><br><img src="http://pic128.huitu.com/res/20190901/571787_20190901124015978020_1.jpg" alt="中秋"></p>]]></content>
    
